{"tid":1562531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"栄光よ香港にあれ (願榮光歸香港 日語版)","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T14:21:42.000Z","uid":90464,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd60abc08e08f6a1650916f34eeafbd9640fba5","tid":1562531,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5uYJ0Mgva4E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5uYJ0Mgva4E&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=fbc339b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5uYJ0Mgva4E</a><br />\n<br />\n《栄光よ香港にあれ  (願榮光歸香港)》<br />\nなぜ 涙止まらぬ  (何以 這土地 淚再流)<br />\nなぜ 怒りを 感じる  (何以 令眾人 亦憤恨)<br />\n頭を上げ 叫びよ 届け  (昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透)<br />\n自由よ、ここにあれ  (盼自由 歸於 這裡)<br />\n<br />\nなぜ 恐れが 残る  (何以 這恐懼 抹不走)<br />\nなぜ 信じて 進んでく  (何以 為信念 從沒退後)<br />\nなぜ 傷ついても 叫んでる  (何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透)<br />\n自由よ 輝け  (建自由 光輝 香港)<br />\n<br />\n星が 落ちる 夜に  (在晚星 墜落 徬徨午夜)<br />\n霧で 角笛が 響く  (迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號角聲)<br />\n自由を！ 集まれ 戦え  (捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對)<br />\n勇気 叡智 消えぬ  (勇氣 智慧 也永不滅)<br />\n<br />\n夜明けだ 香港を 取り戻せ  (黎明來到 要光復 這香港)<br />\nこの時代に 正義を！ 革命を！  (同行兒女 為正義 時代革命)<br />\nどうか 民主よ自由よ 朽ちないで  (祈求 民主與自由 萬世都不朽)<br />\n栄光よ 香港に あれ  (我願榮光歸香港)"},{"pid":"d9576e92bcc5b4188673f5a7378e41bf85c7a37f","tid":1562531,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"bee0026953eb9b7b52d3d298985aaae2e54f5150","tid":1562531,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a181e244695a9460b15c59f440647221d63f0ceb","tid":1562531,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd47cbe6f058de5c4014bbdf4e5f2bda2aa9672","tid":1562531,"uid":90464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52765b83ea253c8401c14497e31f150e717ea924","tid":1562531,"uid":242665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:14:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2bc439447a3384a3fd8f7b761fe7a2f2b039736","tid":1562531,"uid":116530,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"難聽到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2351de9171a03e12d6841df6d720e8ab630eeda2","tid":1562531,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"其實轉外文有D字要修改下先好聽,真接轉字係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4bb565bba5459785b5a374c5e54466de3dbc25","tid":1562531,"uid":265273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06